{"tid":1563722,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"DLLM黃之鋒去德國羅光環！","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:14:45.000Z","uid":206090,"like":21,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a1483570a2007b159dbde25c74068185ab8eb183","tid":1563722,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"節錄自【唔係人人都食到大辣】by 港女德國扮工<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/german.dark.office/posts/3020606241346377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgerman.dark.office%2Fposts%2F3020606241346377&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=6a40d079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/german.dark.office/posts/3020606241346377</a><br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n以前阻街會比人屌，以前推鐵馬都會話暴力，依家呢？因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係人人都可以第一下就食大辣，有啲人由清湯開始食，有啲人由10小辣開始食。</span></strong><br />\n今時今日大部份香港人都食到大辣，但大部分德國人唔係。佢哋仲處於汲收緊香港資訊嘅階段。你無啦啦逼佢食大辣，佢一下子接受唔到。反而黃之鋒呢啲10小辣，已經令德國人流晒眼淚。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>有人話：「外國人示威仲激進啦！」</strong></ins></span><br />\n<blockquote>佢地習慣左示威激進，所以就更覺得黃之鋒呢啲左膠和理非好可愛。德國人唔係反對香港示威者升級，只係佢地更喜歡左膠大愛和理非，「易入口啲」。</blockquote><br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「Dllm黃之鋒唔代表香港人！」</span></strong></ins><br />\n<blockquote>外國媒體如何揀人去代表香港，係唔到我地決定。dllm，黃之鋒之前，係成虫代表緊香港呀，我地有得揀咩？！</blockquote><br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「黃之鋒今次冇份抗爭，唔好衝出黎奶光環！」</span></strong></ins><br />\n<blockquote>嗱，查實佢嘅發言講左兩三次，講自己唔係呢次運動嘅Leader，佢係向外國解釋五大訴求、警暴、新屋嶺發生咩事。大部分德國人講起香港示威就諗起佢，正如大家講起德國，會先諗起「著皮褲、飲啤酒、食香腸」同樣代表唔到德國。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然黃之鋒有冇光環，代唔代表香港，大家都控制唔到，倒不如利用佢嘅影響力。要知道，佢個朵仲響過林鄭，尋日佢仲係同德國外長會面，搞到強國要召德國大使抗議。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢幾千蚊一張來回機票，換來：<br />\n1. 強國揼春<br />\n2. 場內五毛挑機獻醜<br />\n3. 強國人喺柏林上街抗議<br />\n4. 三大報紙頭版（我地兩次眾籌登報，都係登到內頁咋）</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家可以無限loop佢嘅膠事，但喺呢個時候，善用利用借用好過割蓆。</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c616e40746d79d1ed0059bc6e8eee544ebca099","tid":1563722,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">對準政權 遍地開花</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2D3bRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2D3bRU.jpg&h=49b546b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXuufm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXuufm1.jpg&h=98681984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yM2WNBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM2WNBw.jpg&h=9433ed2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zasf29R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzasf29R.jpg&h=aca10195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4ce9e7646619bfac6b7143e648c4ad817c3c3b7","tid":1563722,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"分化撚blocked"},{"pid":"f48374f3d68c01e8d0193b7cf0228e2f189f0a21","tid":1563722,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A